MIPS: retire "asm/llsc.h"

all that "asm/llsc.h" does is just to help inline asm, which can be
stringifyed from "asm/asm.h"

+. Since "asm/asm.h" has all we need, retire "asm/llsc.h"

+. remove unused header file

